OL,3,CSkiers and snowboarders enjoy
OL,4,C'England's longest ski slope'
OL,6,FGregg Easteal was in County Durham
OL,7,Fwhere skiers and snowboarders turned
OL,8,Fout to enjoy the 'Champagne powder'
OL,9,Fcovered slopes
OL,11,FDozens of snow enthusiasts have
OL,12,Fbattled the wintry conditions to enjoy
OL,13,Fa day on the slopes of Weardale Ski
OL,14,FClub, something that is becoming rarer
OL,15,Fdue to climate change.
OL,17,FThe centre based on Fendrith Hill, in
OL,18,FCounty Durham, claims to have the
OL,19,Flongest lift-served ski run in England.
