OL,6,FThe road up to the slopes is so
OL,7,Ftreacherous that those looking to
OL,8,Faccess the club need to complete the
OL,9,Flast mile on foot.
OL,11,FRoy travelled to the ski centre from
OL,12,FSheffield on Tuesday (7 January).
OL,14,FHe told ITV Tyne Tees that the journey
OL,15,Fwas worth it for the "champagne
OL,16,Fpowder", and was even better than the
OL,17,FAlps for him.
