OL,6,FHe said: "Champagne powder boarders
OL,7,Fcall it, when there are all the little
OL,8,Fglistening crystals because it's so
OL,9,Flight and fluffy. You could just jump
OL,10,Finto a load of powder."
OL,12,FMeanwhile Alan, 81, said: "I've always
OL,13,Fenjoyed skiing, so having snow here in
OL,14,FWeardale absolutely great. It's a
OL,15,Freally good day."
