OL,4,C'England's longest ski slope'
OL,6,FLocal skiers do everything they can to
OL,7,Fget to the centre when snow arrives,
OL,8,Fas those from Weardale Ski Club say
OL,9,Fhaving long periods of snow are
OL,10,Fgetting less frequent with changes in
OL,11,Fthe climate.
OL,13,FMilder, wetter, weather often washes
OL,14,Fsnow on the fells away quickly.
OL,16,FSteve Lumb, from the Weardale Ski
OL,17,FClub, said: "They've all been watching
OL,18,Fthe weather itching to get up here and
OL,19,Fwe've finally been able to open today.
